<p>And, here is how I checked those library updates:<br>
<a target="_blank" href="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/920911/35190806-1b299e22-feae-11e7-84e5-ff640572c923.png"><img width="298" alt="2018-01-21 1 16 25" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/920911/35190806-1b299e22-feae-11e7-84e5-ff640572c923.png" style="max-width:100%;"></a></p>
<p><em>If possible this issue should be open to anyone, and whenever anyone has time, those libraries can be updated after checking that the update does not affect this app negatively.</em></p>
<p>(I am not sure it is worth updating the library to <code>-alpha</code> version, as it may not be stable or may have breaking API changes or drastic internal  changes).</p>
<p>What do you think?</p>
